<h2>When is Penn InTouch Available?</h2>
<p>Penn InTouch is normally available 24/7 except to allow for system maintenance between 3:00 AM and 6:00 AM on Mondays. In addition, some functions within Penn InTouch may be unavailable for brief periods during the evenings while we update student data.</p>

